knight fellowships digital media and device convergence knight fellowships digital media and device convergence the semantic web and other forces changing journalism andrew finlayson 2010 knight fellow senior vice president digital media strategies smithgeiger los angeles california andrew finlayson researched the future of digital media and device convergence he explored how four key trends mobile video the semantic web and social media are going to change journalism in the next five years as he researched these trends he also looked entrepreneurship innovation and collaboration in silicon valley and how lessons of the region can be used by media organizations during this time of unprecedented change he shared his insights through the website adigitaljournalist com a digital journalist andrew finlayson's fellowship bio stanford university
